@GoodHamburger.Api_HostAddress = http://localhost:5251

### Listar cardápio
GET {{GoodHamburger.Api_HostAddress}}/api/menu
Accept: application/json

###

### Listar todos os pedidos
GET {{GoodHamburger.Api_HostAddress}}/api/orders
Accept: application/json

###

### Criar pedido — combo completo (20% desconto)
POST {{GoodHamburger.Api_HostAddress}}/api/orders
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "itemIds": ["x-burger", "fries", "soda"]
}

###

### Criar pedido — sanduíche + refrigerante (15% desconto)
POST {{GoodHamburger.Api_HostAddress}}/api/orders
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "itemIds": ["x-bacon", "soda"]
}

###

### Criar pedido — sanduíche + batata (10% desconto)
POST {{GoodHamburger.Api_HostAddress}}/api/orders
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "itemIds": ["x-egg", "fries"]
}

###

### Criar pedido — só sanduíche (sem desconto)
POST {{GoodHamburger.Api_HostAddress}}/api/orders
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "itemIds": ["x-burger"]
}

###

### Buscar pedido por ID (substituir pelo ID real)
GET {{GoodHamburger.Api_HostAddress}}/api/orders/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000
Accept: application/json

###

### Atualizar pedido (substituir pelo ID real)
PUT {{GoodHamburger.Api_HostAddress}}/api/orders/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "itemIds": ["x-bacon", "fries", "soda"]
}

###

### Remover pedido (substituir pelo ID real)
DELETE {{GoodHamburger.Api_HostAddress}}/api/orders/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000

###

### Erro — item duplicado
POST {{GoodHamburger.Api_HostAddress}}/api/orders
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "itemIds": ["x-burger", "x-burger"]
}

###

### Erro — dois sanduíches
POST {{GoodHamburger.Api_HostAddress}}/api/orders
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "itemIds": ["x-burger", "x-bacon"]
}

###

### Erro — pedido sem sanduíche
POST {{GoodHamburger.Api_HostAddress}}/api/orders
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "itemIds": ["fries", "soda"]
}

###
